title: Grateful Dead Live at Cotterell Gym, Colgate University on 1977-11-04
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Good Lovin', Brown Eyed Women, Cassidy, It Must Have Been The Roses, Sunrise, Minglewood Blues, Dupree's Diamond Blues, Let It Grow

Set 2

Samson & Delilah-> Cold Rain & Snow, Playin' In The Band-> Eyes Of The World-> Estimated Prophet-> The Other One-> Drums-> Iko Iko-> Stella Blue-> Playin' In The Band, E: Johnny B. Goode

reviews.review_text:
Water nothing has ever seemed so translucent, it's a certain clarity only an audience recording can bring to the music. I thought I knew everything there was just from hearing soundboards - cohesive, dramatic, full of resonance. Until beginning my foray into the wide plethora of audience tapes. This here is an amazing, quality piece of that journey. Sit with this and enjoy the band quite literally performing behind your head...ZAP!

* Nick, 1/27/2023
